OL,6,FA man with paranoid schizophrenia who
OL,7,Fkilled three pensioners in Exeter over
OL,8,Fallegations he faced negligent
OL,9,Ftreatment from authorities before
OL,10,Ftheir deaths, the Court of Appeal has
OL,11,Fruled.
OL,13,FAlexander Lewis-Ranwell, 32 and from
OL,14,FCroyde in Devon, killed 80-year-old
OL,15,FAnthony Payne with a hammer and
OL,16,Fbludgeoned to death 84-year-old twins
OL,17,FDick and Roger Carter with a shovel in
OL,18,FFebruary 2019.
