OL,3,CMan who killed three pensioners can
OL,4,Ccontinue negligence claims, judges rule
OL,6,FAfter a trial, a jury at Exeter Crown
OL,7,FCourt found the former scaffolder not
OL,8,Fguilty of murder by reason of insanity
OL,9,F` meaning that because of his mental
OL,10,Fillness he did not know at the time of
OL,11,Fthe killings what he was doing was
OL,12,Fwrong.
OL,14,FA judge imposed a hospital order with
OL,15,Frestrictions, with Lewis-Ranwell
OL,16,Fdetained at the high-security
OL,17,FBroadmoor Hospital.
