OL,3,CMan who killed three pensioners can
OL,4,Ccontinue negligence claims, judges rule
OL,6,FIn a majority ruling on Tuesday 20
OL,7,FFebruary, senior judges said Lewis-
OL,8,FRanwell's case against the
OL,9,Forganisations could continue.
OL,11,FLord Justice Underhill, with whom Dame
OL,12,FVictoria Sharp agreed, said he
OL,13,Fbelieved "the considered view of right-
OL,14,Fthinking people would be that someone
OL,15,Fwho was indeed insane should not be
OL,16,Fdebarred from compensation for the
OL,17,Fconsequences of their doing an
OL,18,Funlawful act which they did not know
OL,19,Fwas wrong and for which they,
OL,20,Ftherefore, had no moral culpability".
